Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:17.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.11,0:00:24.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:32.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:34.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:36.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:40.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:41.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:50.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino, Kirino!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.62,0:00:57.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, when Dad was watching you work, he tried to take a picture and got mistaken for a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:01:00.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:08.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He got nervous and was all, "N-No, this is my daughter!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:09.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:12.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:52.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:58.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The president really likes Kanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:00.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to have an interview soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it goes well, they might hire her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like another step to being an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:08.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was a good thing to do that crappy gig.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm going to blow right past your level before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:18.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Kanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:22.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll pass. Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:32.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister would never say "Good morning" or "Thanks" or "Here's yours".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not Kirino.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:36.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That is something else wearing her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:42.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Kirino-chan just feels like thanking you properly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:55.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ew"? You don't need to—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Onii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help last time.{Manami's face.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:04.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:07.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:10.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan, do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:12.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One of Kirino's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:16.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you. My name is Aragaki Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:19.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise! I'm Tamura Manami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:23.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm Kyou-chan's childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:25.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:31.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't really been acting differently...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the usual Kirino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:38.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything were to happen, I would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm her best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:40.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to ask such a weird question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:47.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'll be off, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:48.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:05:00.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did suggest the event, but Miss Kiririn was quite active in the preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:04.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she was forcing herself or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:06.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm just overthinking things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:12.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose it's natural for you to be concerned about Miss Kiririn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:20.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:21.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyoro~n.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:32.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you come to my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:50.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your room's a lot cleaner than last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:53.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I cleaned up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:57.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:00.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that final life counseling you were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's one way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever. Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to buy me an eroge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:25.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'd Never Steal Something Like Onii-chan's Pantsu!!"{Direct reference to Onii-chan no Koto Nanka Zenzen Suki Ja Naindakarane!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:26.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,3D Custom Imouto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,OniPan and CusImo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:31.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of abbreviations...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:35.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to line up for the midnight release and get them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:39.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is seriously your last life counseling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking me to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:46.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want to play them as soon as possible, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:54.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My plan is to sleep in the afternoon until you get it, then play until morning, finishing at least one route.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with you? You'd go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I would. Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:03.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But that store is in Akiba, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:07.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I buy it at midnight, I won't get back until after 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If Dad finds out—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:14.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you status updates on him by phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:19.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play it as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:21.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please? This is the last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please?{うっせー}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:31.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I just need to go buy it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:34.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:40.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Akagi. Can you make it look like I'm staying at your place tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:44.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure. Go get that Tamura-san, eh?{赤城、妄想中}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like he's misunderstanding this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:53.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:05.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these all... Kirino's kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:12.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All customers for the midnight release, line up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone came here on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:28.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is this the end of the line?{In many ways, yes.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kousaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:43.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you to make it look like I'm staying at your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:45.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing buying eroge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long story...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:52.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I thought you were going somewhere nice with Tamura-san!{Ehe.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing buying eroge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:57.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long story...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we both have extenuating circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:06.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we say we never met here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:13.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither you nor I was at a midnight release in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We did not line up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:18.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we did not buy any eroge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:25.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends expect nothing in return!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:30.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Customers with pre-orders for Homoge Club, line up here please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:38.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:41.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what they call a full-on homo game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kousaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are definitely misunderstanding things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:47.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! Look into my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:49.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not homo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, that's a full-on homo game!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:56.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But my sister asked me to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:59.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister is still a middle schooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:04.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, a middle school girl asking her brother to go buy an eroge is totally—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...possible, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you suddenly accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:18.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is full of things that defy all common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I doubted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:23.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:26.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister plays homo games?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister is what they call a fujoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:34.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "fu" as in "wife", but as in "rotten".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:40.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't help but shriek in joy when she fantasizes about men in love or in intimate relations.{I think we can turn this into "She says that..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:46.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's all like, "I like homos! I like them a lot! I love them!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they clapping at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:59.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, I got it. Don't mind me and get into that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting! Time for the midnight release!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:11.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please follow directions from the staff for your purchase!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:15.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, first ten people in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pantsu here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan no Pantsu here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:21.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The register is over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:26.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I make the last train...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< Part B >
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< CHANGE STARTS HERE >
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:47.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:55.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the game, but the line was really long...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:58.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The last train left before I got out of the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:02.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... you can't get back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:04.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:06.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:11.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So... there's no way for you to get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you at least get back by morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:26.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean leave it—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:30.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find some way to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay up and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:45.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please lend me that bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:46.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:49.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return it to you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:56.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, you were the homo behind me in line?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:57.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:00.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister is waiting for me at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need that bike for her sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:11.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have some extreme circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:21.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:24.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:25.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:34.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought the same game as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been buying it since the first volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:38.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my favorite series.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:46.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one who loves this game can be bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:54.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing a game in public adds some spice to the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How big is your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:32.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'd make you a pair of nekomimi, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:36.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry up and tell me how big your fat, round head is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, it's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just mail me about that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:46.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The server is down tonight for maintenance, so I thought I would leave a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:51.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have asked tomorrow, but I figured I might as well ask tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:54.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to see you up this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who did you think I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:13.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredible that Nii-san has enough patience to put up with your insolence.{Dammit, I want to be called Nii-san.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:14.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And can you stop calling him that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:18.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:20.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, it's gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:24.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And he goes all dere when you say it. It's just gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:26.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:27.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:30.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be calling him something different soon enough.{Dammit, I want to be called Senpai.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< MORE CHANGES HERE >
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:38.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Nii-san I said hi when he gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\fax0.1\c&Ha670e9&\3c&Hfafafa&\fs40\frz10.415\pos(562,264)}Kyousuke
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out your window.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< MORE CHANGES HERE >
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all sweaty now, so I'm going to take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:47.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:52.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to play together? It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:54.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:59.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it. I can't see the screen if I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's installed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:06.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd Never Steal Something Like Onii-chan's Pantsu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:12.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This game only has one heroine, but it has a lot of routes for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:16.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time you clear a route, you get more choices and the ending changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just like most other games.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:25.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are minigames throughout it, and based on the items you get in them, different flags get raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:31.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:33.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's way too sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:34.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:37.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they're separated by the grave or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They can always talk on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:41.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! You're so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:42.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lonely not being able to see each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Try putting yourself in their shoes!{Atticus Finch?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it that way, this is a lonely ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:54.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I need to get the other branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:06.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's the end. I can go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:10.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Life counseling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:17.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You said that this was the end of your life counseling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought your eroge for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:22.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not over yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, what is it? Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it growing?{PanSto poster at the bottom there?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, it's been nine months since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:45.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what happened that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:56.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there was something embarrassing that I couldn't show you that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:19:04.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You kept it a secret, and you didn't make fun of me, and you helped me out a lot, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:09.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She has something even crazier than anime and eroge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:14.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing... but I'll let you see.{Nani woooooooo?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< MORE CHANGES HERE >
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:22.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:27.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you... eat poop?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:30.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I would!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of question is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:41.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what "toro" was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:46.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I loved the artist, so I—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:48.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Stop! Stop talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we move on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:54.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'll show you next is the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:56.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:13.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more normal than I thought it would be,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no way anything my sister owns is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:19.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially that. That album looks bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:22.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to know what's in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:22.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:25.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This album...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:27.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< BRANCH POINT: ALL CHANGES FROM HERE >
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:34.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:42.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, at least look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Paper:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Report Card
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,[Name of school. Don't really need it.]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Name: Kousaka Kirino}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A report card?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:55.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I started track is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Report card:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Language: Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mathematics: Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Science: Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Social studies: Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Music: Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Art: Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Physical Education: Let's try harder.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:02.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I was really slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:07.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got really pissed off and started practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:15.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my badges from sports festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:19.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never told anyone about this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:27.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,when I'm feeling down or in a slump, I open this up and get pissed off and think "Don't look down on me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:29.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:32.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably can't beat you in a race anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:36.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:38.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:46.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,These and those are really important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:52.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd help me protect my collection, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:53.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:56.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be doing that from now on too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:21:59.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:01.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your brother, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:03.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like I can help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:07.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:09.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:12.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:14.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your final life counseling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:17.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:19.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:23.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:25.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a lot better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:28.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:32.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:33.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:39.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Aniki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:44.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And just like that, my sister disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:22:55.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kirino?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:56.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning practice again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:22:58.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:22:59.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.34,0:23:05.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. She said she'd tell you herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:06.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:09.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino left for America this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:13.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was scouted by a famous track coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:15.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:20.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was invited when she was at training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:23.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be training there until she enters high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:27.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wanted to see how far she could go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:30.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I was against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:34.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could let my 14-year-old daughter go somewhere I can't keep track of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:37.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I wouldn't give a single yen for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:40.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But she pulled out her bankbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:45.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Using her savings from working and the royalties from her book, she bought her own ticket to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:47.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"You don't have any problems with it now, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.62,0:23:51.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, her stubbornness is something to be reckoned with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.59,0:23:57.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.87,0:24:09.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.29,0:24:11.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.26,0:24:16.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your all...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.36,0:24:19.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.36,0:24:29.65,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}School Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.39,0:24:32.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan, you've changed a lot recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.02,0:24:34.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Like how?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.38,0:24:36.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.03,0:24:38.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nicer now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.20,0:24:39.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.76,0:24:43.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I need to call you Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.69,0:24:45.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything but that, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.57,0:24:49.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.34,0:24:55.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
