Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:24.10,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashiku shinai de donna kao sureba ii no?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:27.40,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta kotoba de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:34.44,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,mienai yo kimi no yokogao
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:46.58,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,dokodakke? nakushita kagi ha mitsukaranai mama de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:53.22,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tameiki... surechigai ni iji hatte tsukarechau
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:02:00.00,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,hon no sukoshi chikaku kimi to no kyori ga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:07.21,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,umaku tsukamenainda ato chotto na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:14.41,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashikushinaide hora mata kizutsukeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:21.25,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta uso de mou ugokenakunatteru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:28.59,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sugu ni ai ni ikitai kedo kotoba ha mitsukaranai shi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:39.10,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,saigo no ichi pe-ji kurai kimi ni ha egao misetai
Comment: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:16.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Translation}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:24.10,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me, I just don't know how to react
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:27.40,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these words piling up,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:34.44,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even see your face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:46.58,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? I lost my key, now I can't find it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:53.22,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh, I'll burn out if I keep acting like this whenever we fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:02:00.00,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're close? I just can't figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:07.21,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how far away I am, even though you're right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:14.41,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me, see? We hurt each other again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:21.25,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these lies piling up, I can't even move
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:28.59,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you now, but I don't know what to say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:39.10,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the end for our story, I want you to see my smile
