Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.93,0:25:24.20,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,アタシらしいって
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.04,0:25:30.17,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,No cry　勇気が要るかな
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.68,0:25:34.98,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,強がり上手で
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.70,0:25:40.28,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,言いたいことも　言えずにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.39,0:25:44.95,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,お早うもなしに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.14,0:25:47.74,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,見送るだけの背中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.00,0:25:50.18,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,聞いてよ　それだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.43,0:25:53.01,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,何かが始まるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.54,0:25:57.99,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,精一杯の人生を　さあ　行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.17,0:26:01.16,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,無駄じゃないこのときめきが
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.36,0:26:03.69,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,道を描いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.25,0:26:09.48,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,精一杯の人生を続けて行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.14,0:26:15.20,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,なんでもかんでも　好きでもいいじゃないのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.20,0:26:19.93,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do the best we can　あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Translation}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.93,0:25:24.20,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,How to be like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.04,0:25:30.17,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,You might need a little courage not to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.68,0:25:34.98,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at acting strong
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.70,0:25:40.28,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,And the things I want to say, I just can't say them
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.39,0:25:44.95,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a "Good morning"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.14,0:25:47.74,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I watch you walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.00,0:25:50.18,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just listened to me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.43,0:25:53.01,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe something would start
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.54,0:25:57.99,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Living life the best you can, come on, go
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.17,0:26:01.16,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,That twinkle in your chest isn't meaningless
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.36,0:26:03.69,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll show you the way
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.25,0:26:09.48,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Living live the best you can, come on, keep going
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.14,0:26:15.20,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything and anything, you can love it all
